.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-CHANGE-APPLY 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.7.4" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-change\-apply \- build a gated apply intent from a reviewed sync plan, and optionally execute it live.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util change apply [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
build a gated apply intent from a reviewed sync plan, and optionally execute it live.
.PP
when a plan is already reviewed and you are ready to emit or execute the apply step.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
build a gated apply intent from a reviewed sync plan, and optionally execute it live.
.EX
grafana-util change apply --plan-file ./sync-plan-reviewed.json --approve
.EE
.PP
build a gated apply intent from a reviewed sync plan, and optionally execute it live.
.EX
grafana-util change apply --plan-file ./sync-plan-reviewed.json --approve --execute-live --allow-folder-delete --profile prod
.EE
